title: MNF Recap; What *YOUUUUUUU* People Don't Realize
itunes:title: MNF Recap; What *YOUUUUUUU* People Don't Realize
description:
A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, Chris Wesseling and Gregg Rosenthal recap the Monday night overtime corker between the Eagles and Giants (5:56). The heroes break down all of the news around the NFL including the latest with the PI rule review (32:05) and Lev Bell going bowling with the flu (37:56). The ATN guys bring back a crowd favorite segment, "What YOUUUUUUUUUU people don't realize" (51:18) and then preview the Ravens-Jets TNF game.
